<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Okla puta hʋchia ma!
 Ʋba Pi̱ki fehna kʋno
 Iloh i̱ yimmi pullashke;
 Ik a̱hli, iloh ahnashke.

[V2]
 Ʋba anumpa fehna kʋt
 Nana moma i̱ shahlishke
 Eho haklo pullakbano,
 Iloh aiahni pullashke.

[V3]
 Anumpa hanta ilʋppa
 Hʋpi chu̱kʋsh fehna hoka,
 Sa nukfokakbano, ahnit,
 Eho pihi̱sa pullashke.

[V4]
 Hatak ithana chia ma!
 Hina hanta achukma ka
 Iloh ia pullakbano
 Hʋchim ahni li fehnʋshke.

[V5]
 Okla eho moma hokʋt
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla hoka,
 Pit iloh ahni pullashke;
 Iloh aiokpahanchashke.

[V6]
 Hatak puta hʋchia ma!
 Yakni achukma fehna ka
 Ia ka aiahni lishke;
 Hʋs siakaiya pullashke.</lyrics>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Okla puta hʋchia ma! ƲIT16</title>
<author>S. W.</author>
